title: French Meadow Bakery and Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Bakery, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. European style cafe and bakery. Prices moderate to expensive depending on day or night. Has vegetarian and vegan lunch and dinner entrees, vegan desserts, vegan soups and sandwiches. Wi-fi access. Also located at Minneapolis/St. Paul MSP International Airport.
